INSERT INTO `v9_news_data` VALUES('104','<span style=\"color: rgb(123, 123, 123); font-family: 微软雅黑, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft Yahei&quot;, &quot;WenQuanYi Micro Hei&quot;, Simsun, sans-serif; font-size: 14px;\">开盖有奖在国内盛行近25年，至今为止还是快消行业的主流促销模式。随之而来的是各种问题的发生，由于促销活动是印刷在包装内，促销的奖项都是固定的，所引的起是促销投放效率低下，促销不精准，费用浪费严重等。由于促销凭证需要回收，中间环节所产生的回收手续费居高不下，回收环节投入人力过多，更致命的促销凭证作假，引发的费用流失严重。这些都是我们心中的痛。</span>\r\n<p style=\"box-sizing: border-box; margin: 2px; padding: 0px; font-size: 14px; line-height: 28px; color: rgb(123, 123, 123); font-family: 微软雅黑, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft Yahei&quot;, &quot;WenQuanYi Micro Hei&quot;, Simsun, sans-serif;\">&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p style=\"box-sizing: border-box; margin: 2px; padding: 0px; font-size: 14px; line-height: 28px; color: rgb(123, 123, 123); font-family: 微软雅黑, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft Yahei&quot;, &quot;WenQuanYi Micro Hei&quot;, Simsun, sans-serif; text-align: center;\"><img alt=\"\" src=\"/touyun/uploadfile/2018/0414/20180414102321484.png\" style=\"width: 352px; height: 264px;\" /></p>\r\n<p style=\"box-sizing: border-box; margin: 2px; padding: 0px; font-size: 14px; line-height: 28px; color: rgb(123, 123, 123); font-family: 微软雅黑, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft Yahei&quot;, &quot;WenQuanYi Micro Hei&quot;, Simsun, sans-serif;\">&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p style=\"box-sizing: border-box; margin: 2px; padding: 0px; font-size: 14px; line-height: 28px; color: rgb(123, 123, 123); font-family: 微软雅黑, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft Yahei&quot;, &quot;WenQuanYi Micro Hei&quot;, Simsun, sans-serif;\">&nbsp;</p>\r\n<span style=\"color: rgb(123, 123, 123); font-family: 微软雅黑, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft Yahei&quot;, &quot;WenQuanYi Micro Hei&quot;, Simsun, sans-serif; font-size: 14px;\">随着移动互联网的发展，